rd with Ariston, Crescentian, Eutychian, Urban, Vitalis, Justus, Felicissimus, Felix, and Symphorosa. None is individually very famous."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mary Gagnon was born in 1221, in Devon, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son. She died in her hometown."},"et":{"1221–":"1221–Surnud","1246–1327":"1246–1327","1221–Female":"1221–Surnud","1327":"1327","1246":"1246","1221":"1221","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1221–":"1221–Kuollut","1246–1327":"1246–1327","1221–Female":"1221–Kuollut","1327":"1327","1246":"1246","1221":"1221","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1221–":"1221–Décédée","1246–1327":"1246–1327","1221–Female":"1221–Décédée","1327":"1327","1246":"1246","1221":"1221","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mary Gagnon est née en 1221, à Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils. Elle est décédée dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"1221–":"1221–Verstorben","1246–1327":"1246–1327","1221–Female":"1221–Verstorben","1327":"1327","1246":"1246","1221":"1221","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Mary Gagnon wurde 1221 in Devon, England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hatte mindestens 1 Sohn. Sie starb in ihrem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"1221–":"1221–Desede","1246–1327":"1246–1327","1221–Female":"1221–Desede","1327":"1327","1246":"1246","1221":"1221","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1221–":"1221–elhunyt","1246–1327":"1246–1327","1221–Female":"1221–elhunyt","1327":"1327","1246":"1246","1221":"1221","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, Anglia, United Kingdom"},"id":{"1221–":"1221–Telah Meninggal","1246–1327":"1246–1327","1221–Female":"1221–Telah Meninggal","1327":"1327","1246":"1246","1221":"1221","Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Devon, Inggris, United Kingdom"},"it":{"1221–":"1221–Deceduta","1246–1327":"1246–1327","1221–Female":"122